name: Catch the Fish (khawaja_azfar)
description: Hello guys!, this is frank. He a labor, who work in the city for his living and he is very busy in his life. His work life make him angry and frustrated, so he decided to went to him lake house to relax himself and to gain mental peace, his lake house is 6 hour drive from the city, he is afraid to travel this much far but at last he decided to give it a short and he went to lake house but he forgot to take food supplies with his. Now either he has to travel back 6 house to city or to go for fishing in the lake , so after thinking we went for fishing but don't much how to catch the fish so we have to help him. Lets go help him...
